posting_body: ['Love where you live; come home to Amanda Regency Apartments', 'Amanda Regency, the very best in San Fernando Valley apartments, is perfectly situated in the heart of Lake Balboa in the San Fernando Valley.', 'Here you can enjoy both convenience and serenity.', 'Our units are spacious and functional and offer multiple floor plans.', 'The community offers a fitness center, clubhouse and pool with breathtaking views.', "Enjoy nearby Lake Balboa's parks and recreation with everything from fishing to bike and boat rentals.", 'Take your four-legged friends for a walk through the trails; or if you want to let them loose, take a stroll in the nearby dog park.', 'Variety is endless in the area with wonderful shopping at the Topanga Mall and countless boutiques and dining options on Ventura Boulevard.', 'With easy access to the 101 and 405 freeways, you are only minutes away from enjoying a show at the Hollywood Bowl.', 'Love where you live; come home to Amanda Regency Apartments.', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.', 'Please contact our leasing office for current pricing and specials.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 33', 'OR Text', '33', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'Want more info on this unit?', 'See the link (below):', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 883 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Newly Renovated Units Will Have:', '* White Shaker Cabinets in Kitchen and Baths', '* Quartz Counters in Kitchen and Baths', '* AT&T Fiber throughout Building( WIFI)', '* Brand New Vinyl Plank Flooring', '* Pool, BBQ, Parking, Pet Friendly', '* Brand New Stainless Steel Appliances', '* Central A/C', 'Community Amenities', '- Laundry Facility/ Every Floor', '- Pool/ Heated all year round', '- Fitness Center', '- Controlled Access Parking', '- Controlled Entry to Building', 'Pet Policy', 'Breed Restrictions, Call for more information.', 'Income Requirements:', '3x the Rent.', 'Driving Directions', 'X-street is Vanowen.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday - Sunday 9:00am - 6:00pm', 'Amanda Regency', '6805 Louise Ave., Van Nuys, CA, 91406', 'Photos displayed are a representation of the community but may not be of the exact apartment.', 'Availability and rental rates are updated daily, and conditions are subject to change without notice.', 'Please contact the property for current availability and pricing.', 'Gvq4seW6ag']
